The paper discusses the challenges of monitoring and managing machine learning models in production, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also addresses issues related to software engineering (cs.SE) and security (cs.CR) in the context of ML deployments. Additionally, the paper employs diagnostic methods and statistical techniques, which are commonly used in data science (cs.DS).
